*Telefon* je neophodan za komunikaciju. (The telephone is necessary for communication.)

Ona je uzela *telefon* da pozove svoju majku. (She took the phone to call her mother.)

*Telefoniranje* je postalo vrlo popularno. (Telephoning has become very popular.)

Moj školski prijatelj i ja smo stalno *telefonirali*. (My school friend and I were constantly on the phone.)

Ona je uvek uz *telefon*, čak i kada ide na put. (She is always on the phone, even when she is traveling.)